column5: Looks like dem herrin's are getting larger...Thanks for the video son...
Looks like fun. We had our first ice outing with the grandkids    Caught a few dinks and a migraine. Best moment was DeeDee getting her foot stuck in the hole
Nice herring. They sure would be getting kept for bait if legal.  Cheers

Nice herring. They sure would be getting kept for bait if legal.  Cheers  When I get the 2lbders, They go into the oven, backs split, splash of liquid smoke, fresh cracked pepper and sea salt, and get baked til dried out and put on crackers,
Great vid B. Glad to see you got out.  The snow stopped me right in my tracks. 24 inches plus in Haliburton made it almost impossible to get to my back lakes.
Great video bri!!  I wish I could have joined you!!  I'll be out next weekend Saturday and Sunday
aaaah herring. Is there an easier fish on earth to catch? I guess that's why they had to be protected. Aggressive little buggers.Nice video Brian

So after racking my brain why I couldnt  get sound on my video, asking the guys that know, I did some searching on upgrades. I found one but man what a shister site. making money off a free upload. So go searching some more and found my up grade.   This is the live reel of the morning.     Im looking forward to more now.  This high teq stuff hurts me brain.
